A Global Approach for Better Outcomes












Market Commentary:
Second Quarter 2017 by Ben Lavine


 










3D delivers the benefits of exchange-traded funds with uncompromising customer loyalty, personalized guidance and innovative solutions.


3D delivers the benefits of exchange-traded funds with uncompromising customer loyalty, personalized guidance and innovative solutions.



more







Investment Philosophy
Is rooted in our history as a DFA Advisor that transitioned to ETF Strategist. We believe in efficient markets, fundamental asset allocation and the benefits of global diversification.


Investment Process
Delivers strategic portfolios designed and managed to target a rate of return. We utilize fundamentally weighted indices to access strategic beta and strategically tilt allocation based on our view of macro economic conditions.


Why ETFs?
Advances in technology have created a highly effective instrument to access our full range of asset classes. The Exchange Traded Fund delivers substantive benefits of liquidity, transparency, tax-efficiency and lower costs when compared to other financial instruments.


Portfolio Solutions  
We offer a range of risk-based and target date portfolio options. Our target date families feature risk-adjusted glide paths as well as the first co-managed target date series of its kind, which integrates strategic and tactical investment management disciplines. 


Advisor Solutions
Practice management efficiencies are delivered through outsourced portfolio management solutions. We specialize in practice growth and value-creating strategies across the wealth management, qualified plan and retirement income market segments.


Access to 3D
Advisors work with 3D in a multitude of ways; direct through our TAMP, major platforms, unitized models and CITs, with share classes for both fee-based and commission-based advisors.




Is rooted in our history as a DFA Advisor that transitioned to ETF Strategist. We believe in efficient markets, fundamental asset allocation and the benefits of global diversification.







