3d Asset Management, Inc Buys iShares Edge MSCI USA Momentum Factor, PowerShares S&P 500 ...


July 19, 2017, 04:38:05 PM EDT
By insider, GuruFocus









































Shutterstock photo


3d Asset Management, IncNew Purchases: MTUM , SPLV ,Added Positions: MUB , VTV, VEA,Reduced Positions:DLS, EES, VOT, QQQ, IJT, EZM, GMM, GWX, DNL, IEMG,For the details of 3D ASSET MANAGEMENT, INC's stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=3D+ASSET+MANAGEMENT%2C+INCThese are the top 5 holdings of 3D ASSET MANAGEMENT, INCWisdomTree International SmallCap Fund ( DLS ) - 518,214 shares, 22.9% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 3.86%WisdomTree U.S. SmallCap Earnings Fund ( EES ) - 953,507 shares, 19.9% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 2.13%iShares Edge MSCI USA Momentum Factor ( MTUM ) - 334,545 shares, 18.9% of the total portfolio. New PositionVanguard Value ETF - DNQ ( VTV ) - 295,053 shares, 18.11% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 1.01%iShares National Muni Bond ( MUB ) - 77,773 shares, 5.44% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 4.36%New Purchase: iShares Edge MSCI USA Momentum Factor ( MTUM )3d Asset Management, Inc initiated holdings in iShares Edge MSCI USA Momentum Factor. The purchase prices were between $81.8 and $90.79, with an estimated average price of $86.46. The stock is now traded at around $91.98. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 18.9%. The holdings were 334,545 shares as of 2017-06-30.New Purchase: PowerShares S&P 500 Low Volatility Portfolio (SPLV)3d Asset Management, Inc initiated holdings in PowerShares S&P 500 Low Volatility Portfolio. The purchase prices were between $43.19 and $45.69, with an estimated average price of $44.29. The stock is now traded at around $45.03. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.97%. The holdings were 34,804 shares as of 2017-06-30.List of 52-Week LowsList of 3-Year LowsList of 5-Year LowsPremium MembersThis article first appeared on GuruFocus .



